95
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,830
Naozaj to môžem zjesť?

96
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:55,529
Dostanem k tomuto ešte jeden zadarmo?

97
00:09:58,299 --> 00:10:00,110
